Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Hazards of ballet dancing
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z98ck
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Dec 1975
Ballet dancers and sports players suffer physical damage from their professions. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less